createproject text: This is the Projects page, inside this page an user can create new projects filling the following formulary.
guide text: Here you have an explanation about how this Web App works
incomeexpenses1 text: Expenses section, inside a project, will show buttons to add incomes and expenses to this project, this data will be displayed inside a monthly bar chart.
incomeexpenses2 text: Below the monthly chart will be displayed a top of membre's expenses and a table that contains all incomes and expenses of the proyect order by date.
intro text: You are inside Project Expenses Manager, a Web App that provide a place in which you can storage and manage the different expenses and incomes that your proyects has produced. In addition, we will display all the data stored in a simple way, making easier to know the status of your projects.
language text: This Web has been provided with two differents languages, Spanish and English. This language is first selected by taking the default language of user navigator. However, it can be change with the button in the corner.
loginregister text: First, if you want to user our system, you will need to register if you don't have an accout or indentify yourself using the Login page.
members text: Members section will show a table that display all the members belonged to the project, inside this section you can add new members, promote them to managers, see their expenses or expell them.
myexpenses text: Finally we have My Expenses page, this page will show a list of proyects in which the user has expenses with these displayed with a monthly chart and a table.

profile text: This is the Profile page, inside this page, an user can modify the data provided in register and also can delete the actual account used.
projectconfig text: Configuration section will show a formulary in which you can change name, category and image of the proyect, also it provide a delete button to erase the project.
projectcreated text: Once you create a project, it will appear inside your projects section with two buttons, one of them to enter inside the project and the other to delete it.
